Loving this first weekend of Baseball!!
#stlcards
I love watching baseball and it's even more fun when you also play fantasy baseball!! Going to be a fun year!!

Nothing quite like watching the Cardinals on opening day especially when they are at home. Very cool tributes to #4 #5 and #50
Three legends for the Red Birds. It was also great to see some of the greats of the past make their yearly appearance!
